        "faq_1_title": "How do I get more generation quota?",
        "faq_1_desc": "You receive a free quota upon registration. Once used up, click your avatar and choose \"Upgrade Plan\" to unlock Plus / Pro / Ultra with more quota and advanced models.",
        "faq_2_title": "What file formats and sizes are supported?",
        "faq_2_desc": "Supports .docx (Word), .txt (plain text), and .md (Markdown) up to 100MB. Legacy .doc format is not supported — please save as .docx first.",
        "faq_3_title": "Will math formulas in my document be preserved?",
        "faq_3_desc": "Yes. LaTeX formulas ($...$ inline, $$...$$ block) are supported. When uploading .docx, Word equations are auto-extracted and converted to LaTeX, and render correctly in the exported Word file.",
        "faq_4_title": "What if I'm not happy with the result?",
        "faq_4_desc": "Click \"Customize\" to adjust typography settings and regenerate. You can also download the .docx and fine-tune manually in Word. For long documents, use a high-quality model (Gemini Pro) for best structure recognition.",
